frontmatter.description: I made a cake and two kinds of ice cream, from scratch, for my daughter's birthday. The process of making a plan, adapting, executing, delivering, and being validated highlighted how important it is to feel fulfilled, both personally and professionally.
frontmatter.title: Personal and Professional Fulfillment through Cake and Ice Cream

nodes.excerpt: I daughter turned four at the beginning of this year, and I made her a cake and two kinds of ice cream. From scratch. I’m no kitchen wizard…
